{"settings":"{
  "[dart]": {
    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
    "editor.formatOnType": true,
    "editor.rulers": [80],
    "editor.selectionHighlight": false,
    "editor.suggest.snippetsPreventQuickSuggestions": false,
    "editor.suggestSelection": "first",
    "editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
    "editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false
  },
  "editor.fontFamily": "fira code",
  "terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "MesloLGS NF",
  "terminal.integrated.fontSize": 14,
  "terminal.integrated.rendererType": "auto",
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "editor.codeLensFontFamily": "fira code",
  "editor.fontLigatures": true,
  "editor.tabSize": 2,
  "[typescriptreact]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
  },
  "[typescript]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
  },
  "telemetry.enableTelemetry": false,
  "telemetry.enableCrashReporter": false,
  "editor.suggestSelection": "first",
  "vsintellicode.modify.editor.suggestSelection": "automaticallyOverrodeDefaultValue",
  "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
  "files.associations": {
    "*.pl": "prolog"
  },
  "dart.previewLsp": true,
  "files.exclude": {
    "**/.classpath": true,
    "**/.project": true,
    "**/.settings": true,
    "**/.factorypath": true
  },
  "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
  "liveServer.settings.donotShowInfoMsg": true,
  "gruvboxMaterial.darkWorkbench": "flat",
  "bracket-pair-colorizer-2.colors": ["#d8a657", "#d3869b", "#7daea3"],
  "bracket-pair-colorizer-2.showBracketsInGutter": true,
  "importCost.largePackageColor": "#ea6962",
  "importCost.mediumPackageColor": "#d8a657",
  "importCost.smallPackageColor": "#a9b665",
  "material-icon-theme.activeIconPack": "react",
  "prettier.jsxSingleQuote": true,
  "prettier.singleQuote": true,
  "workbench.colorTheme": "Gruvbox Material Dark",
  "workbench.editorAssociations": [
    {
      "viewType": "jupyter.notebook.ipynb",
      "filenamePattern": "*.ipynb"
    }
  ],
  "[svelte]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "svelte.svelte-vscode"
  },
  "window.zoomLevel": 2,
  "editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled": true,
  "Lua.telemetry.enable": false,
  "terminal.integrated.automationShell.linux": "/bin/zsh",
  "terminal.external.linuxExec": "alacritty",
  "svg.preview.mode": "svg"
}
"}
